dct_title_s: Location Plan of Proposed Bulkhead Under Project 110 in the Bayhead-Manasquan Canal
dct_description_sm: Map covers area from the Metedeconk River to the Atlantic Ocean in Point Pleasant Borough. Map depicts the propose 2450 lin. Ft. bulkhead on each side of the canal in addition to the 2450 lin. Ft. bulkheads built in 1934 and 1935.
